      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greenlawn%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The town’s 19th‑century pickle farms still inspire the annual Pickle Festival, held each year at the historic John Gardiner Farm.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        13
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greenlawn%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Greenlawn‑Centerport Historical Association was founded in 1973 to research, collect, and preserve the area’s history.",
